             were indicted for <rs id="t18290409-304-off1722" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290409-304-off1722" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290409-304-off1722" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290409-304-cd1723" type="crimeDate">1st of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290409-304-off1722 t18290409-304-cd1723"></join>, 36 curb-chains, value 12s.; 73 curb-books, value 3s., and 1 handkerchief, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18290409-304-victim2796" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Benton
                  <interp inst="t18290409-304-victim2796" type="surname" value="Benton"></interp>
